SELECT t1."Id", t1."Title", t1."Description", t1."DueDate", t1."IsCompleted", t1."UserId", t1."CategoryId", t1."Priority", t1."Progress", t1."Notes", t0."TagId", t0."TaskId"
FROM (
    SELECT t."Id", t."Title", t."Description", t."DueDate", t."IsCompleted", t."UserId", t."CategoryId", t."Priority", t."Progress", t."Notes"
    FROM "Tasks" AS t
    ORDER BY t."Id"
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t1
LEFT JOIN "TaskTags" AS t0 ON t1."Id" = t0."TaskId"
ORDER BY t1."Id", t0."TaskId"
